    "Our study refers to Beck et al. (2010) to use the staggered DID method to centralize the policy time (i.e., the time of each period minus the time of their policy implementation).",
    "We establish the dynamic model in the following way:",
    "where Green × Time is a dummy variable.",
    "If the enterprise issued green bonds in the tτ period, the value is 1; otherwise, it is 0.",
    "For example, when τ = 2, the dummy vari- able indicates that the enterprise issued green bonds in the second period, which measures the effect of the second year after the issuance of green bonds."
